speech.p: May I draw my hon. Friend's attention to early-day motion 180, which refers to the sad death of Dr. Alison Des Forges? Dr. Des Forges met a number of hon. Members the day before she was killed a couple of weeks ago. She was unquestionably one of the world's leading authorities on the great lakes region. Will my hon. Friend join me and the House in sending her condolences to Dr. Des Forges's family?
